    "description": "Are you a skilled E-commerce Executive looking for your next big career move? Vision Express India Asia Pacific Associates in Vadodara offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Vision Express India Asia Pacific Associates:\nVision Express India Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Vision Express India Asia Pacific Associates!",
